		"name": "TaskForge — API Collection",
		"description": "Full API collection for TaskForge after Phase 3 session management & hardening.\n\nRun the Auth folder first (Register or Login) to populate token/userId variables, then use the Tasks folder.\n\nAuthenticated requests include an explicit Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}} header.\n\nPhase 3 changes:\n- Refresh token rotation (new token on each refresh)\n- /me endpoint uses JWT auth (no query param)\n- All task endpoints require authentication\n- Security response headers (Cache-Control, CSP)\n- Refresh token reuse detection",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
